description:
Allen Institute October 2019 Mouse extracellular electrophysiology data, collected under analogous conditions to the two-photon Brain Observatory imaging experiments, with mice shown a subset of stimuli with a higher number of repeats. 

For more information, see https://portal.brain-map.org/explore/circuits/visual-coding-neuropixels

Data are subject to Allen Institute Terms of Use policy, available at: http://www.alleninstitute.org/legal/terms-use/
